data.description: Beautiful remodeled 2-bedroom 2 bath home. New roof, plumbing, electrical, central heat and air, flooring, doors and windows! Brand new kitchen with range and dishwasher, granite countertops and cabinets. Master has a double vanity with granite top and a shower. Second bathroom has a tub & shower combo and vanity with granite top. Bedrooms have high ceilings & living/dining/kitchen have vaulted ceilings. Quant laundry room with Washer and dryer hookups are hidden away behind folding doors that also conceal tankless hot water heater. A covered entry with concrete also a rear deck. Large backyard partially fenced with plenty of room. Age, sq ft and lot size should be verified by the buyer.
